</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a big investor who cares ab=
out environmental, social and governance issues, one thing that you might d=
o is refuse to invest in companies that mine thermal coal. This way, you wi=
ll not have any thermal coal in your portfolio and you will feel good about=
 yourself. Also if a lot of big investors refuse to invest in coal miners, =
that will raise the cost of capital of coal miners, which will lead to less=
 coal mining, or that is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/25892760.281658/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGlj=
bGVzLzIwMjEtMDctMDgvc29tZW9uZS1pcy1nb2luZy10by1kcmlsbC10aGUtb2lsP2NtcGlkPUJ=
